# Git Versioning Skill Equivalent

- Use this workflow when repository setup, status checks, or prompt-based commits are needed.
- Keep the workspace under git.
- After a prompt changes the workspace, run `./scripts/commit-prompt-state.ps1`.
- Give each personality its own `persona/<slug>` branch.
- Keep `.ai/SHARED_LEARNINGS.md` updated and present across personality branches.
- Use `./scripts/sync-personality-branches.ps1` when `main` and `persona/*` branches need one batch GitHub sync.
- Keep Copilot, Claude Code, and Cursor customizations aligned and listed in `SUPPORTED.md`.